@startuml
title AD-09 Configure unified mode (User vs System)
skinparam linetype ortho

|User|


start
|User|
  :Toggle Unified Mode;

|System|
  if (Enabled?) then (yes)
    :Require selection of focusCategoryId and optional breakCategoryId;
  else (no)
    :Persist disabled; no auto switching;
    stop
  endif

|User|
  :Select focus/break categories;

|System|
  if (Categories selected?) then (yes)
    :Persist configuration;
  else (no)
    :Keep disabled and prompt to select categories;
  endif

stop

@enduml

